headline: Teradyne Leans Into AI Test Demand With New Data Center Venture
summary: Teradyne (NasdaqGS:TER) reports strong quarterly results and ties performance to artificial intelligence demand in semiconductor test and robotics. The company issues guidance that it states is ahead of market expectations, citing AI related orders as a key driver. Teradyne announces a new joint venture with MultiLane to deliver high speed test solutions for the AI data center market. Teradyne operates at the intersection of semiconductor testing, industrial automation, and robotics, all...
